bug.short_desc: Levels can be dragged to Optional Y Series Grouping but "Optional Y Series Grouping" is not listed in the context menu [13]

long_desc.thetext:
Created attachment 86802 screenshot
Description: Levels can be dragged to Optional Y Series Grouping but "Optional Y Series Grouping" is not listed in the context menu.
Build number: 2.3.3.v20080114-0800
Steps to reproduce: 1. New a chart binding to a cube. 2. Select one level
Expected result: "Optional Y Series Grouping" is listed in the context menu.
Actual result: See the screenshot.
Error log: N/A
Not a bug. Optional Y Series Grouping is exactly "group the Y series" Please have a look at the spec.
It's not a bug. "Use to group Y series" means y series grouping.
